---
title: "_onFeedInfoUpdate (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_super: super._onFeedInfoUpdate(asset, isRemoved)
    q_super --> q_check_live: check live auction constraints
    q_check_live --> q_revert: (asset == assetOut and liveAuctionExists) or auctionStarts[asset] != 0
    q_revert --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_live --> [*]: no live auction conflict

    note right of q_check_live
        INV-001: Feed info cannot be updated for assets with live auctions
        INV-002: If asset is assetOut, no feed update while any auction is live
    end note
